[{"url_token": "hxx-39-92", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "771943087", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "771943087", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "但是骑行头盔主要是应付摔车<br>带钢盔被石头杂不照样死 好的骑行头盔嘛  赛事都用骑行头盔自然有它的道理  买贵点不就好了大厂研发顶级头盔用辣么多钱也不是白用的 头盔碎裂容易造成二次伤害  想泡沫一样的东西主要是吸震 比较不容易造成二次伤害", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "知乎用户i7brWp", "author_id": "90564e28d7c0491d6075edec32d07a90", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "zheng-jet", "headline": "non", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "75057924", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "75057924", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "骑行头盔没这么差吧，以前很多摔过的朋友都是头盔裂了人没事。和开车一个道理，硬件安全性再高也抵不过技术差。所以除非你玩FR或者DH，骑行头盔完全够用", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "WaterDrinker", "author_id": "6b6d466568aa361c6714f5670e9deedc", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "li-yang-77-85-1", "headline": "The art of generalship does not age", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "75174118", "reply_comment_id": "75057924", "reply_root_comment_id": "75057924", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>首先技术肯定是关键，尤其是DH(所以我坚决不和玩DH的朋友去作死)</p><p>头盔呢，防擦，不防撞，先举个栗子</p><p>有兴趣你去看一下这条新闻，<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//news.qq.com/a/20130722/000389.htm\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">北京驴友沿川藏线骑车进藏被落石击中身亡(图)_新闻</a></p><p>这个人在路边写自己名字的涂鸦我都看见过，所以印象很深，这就是戴着头盔出事的。</p><p>如果换个角度，从物理的角度谈，就是动量和冲量的混合计算，中学水平就该明白......</p><p>自重越大，受到的冲击力会小，就像生铁和铁砧的关系一样，铁砧越重，受力越小。我那钢盔的自重，就是最好的缓冲。</p><p>当然那种玩意不是什么人都顶得了，所以我推荐安全帽，防砸性能，缓冲性能比单车头盔强多了，还便宜，何乐而不为</p><p>所以很多淘宝视频拿大榔头砸头盔，用来反映质量好，没错</p><p>有本事戴在头上，砸一砸2333333</p><p>其实我主要的意思是，头盔不是万能的.....尤其是怕砸</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "Lee General", "author_id": "91195b0dfbe3baae8c54f415f59b8c08", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "BlueJay", "headline": "Carpe Diem", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "71057233", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "71057233", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "很多骑川藏的新手，都会干一件事<br>在第一天骑完以后，去雅安市邮局，不是去找邮戳<br>是去把后背上的包寄回家........<br>--------------------------<br>我就干过这种事儿，哈哈", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "Jo Bao", "author_id": "fba4a6e8f8c6fd1a6b9056ec32d4d28f", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "yu-zhe-zhi-ying", "headline": "80后普通青年", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "71047881", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "71047881", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "自行车头盔的原理就是在碰撞的时候碎散来吸收冲击的，所以肯定不能用锤子砸。而且长途骑行更看重的是头盔的轻便，安全帽是更安全，甚至全包覆的摩托车头盔也更结识，但你戴着骑个150公里，脖子就不是你的了", "like_count": 5, "author_name": "愚者之影", "author_id": "4607dd195ea8f86f0ef63fe1ae18a6d9", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "li-yang-77-85-1", "headline": "The art of generalship does not age", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "71227097", "reply_comment_id": "71047881", "reply_root_comment_id": "71047881", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "对，所以我上坡戴自行车盔，下坡戴钢盔2333", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "Lee General", "author_id": "91195b0dfbe3baae8c54f415f59b8c08", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "wu-wei-lin-51", "headline": "离我水果摊远点儿", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "70578213", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "70578213", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "很有用，谢谢", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "炜林", "author_id": "52cb5a2f966f24a70091e1d66dca76b8", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}]